Overall the hotel is excellent value for money, close to town, pretty surroundings.. near the main train station and you couldn't ask for money for that price.	The location is good however there are hotels nearby of a higher star rating for the same price.	For the price, there are other options in Rome that will be better, we stayed in one on our return back to Rome.	We booked through Expedia and paid a total of 162 Euro for a three night stay, which is an unbeatable price for the location!